comment: Capela (HOU) and Gobert (UTA) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
Capela (HOU) and Hood (UTA) briefly engage and separate following the screen.
Ingles (UTA) makes contact to Harden's (HOU) wrist that affects his driving shot attempt.
Ingles (UTA) makes marginal contact with Beverley (ATL).
Capela (HOU) makes incidental contact with Hayward (UTA) that does not affect his SQBR.
Hood (UTA) makes body contact with Harden (HOU) that affects his jump shot attempt.
Gordon (HOU) makes contact to Ingles' (UTA) arm that affects his ability to control the pass.
Hayward (UTA) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Beverley (HOU) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Capela (HOU) sets the screen on Hood (UTA) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Capela (HOU) makes contact to Gobert's (UTA) arms that affects his shot attempt.
LO SLA shows Gobert (UTA) make contact with Harrell's (HOU) body that affects his SQBR on the shot attempt.
Beverley (HOU) commits a take foul on Hayward (UTA).
Harrell (HOU) firms up his position and sets the screen on Hood (UTA).
